 evolved yet another unique mechanism to cope with sperm competition deserves more investigations.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Fasel, Nicolas Jean", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Helfenstein, Fabrice", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Buff, Samuel", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Richner, Heinz", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/1d620955ed46055a5b9cd87e043d58d7", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/cc785d03168ba3dea04db272f87bd845fcab908cb168011ed39ccfa27ccd74b2", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/G7BKNCEN", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/G7BKNCEN", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/dae792a88e7ccb20aaba006505ee19b4!/b25047-27507", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "5", "pages": "904-910", "title": "Theriogenology", "volume": "83"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/1d620955ed46055a5b9cd87e043d58d7"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:G7BKNCEN"}, {"identifier": "10.1016/j.theriogenology.2014.11.030"}], "communities": [{"id": "biosyslit"}, {"id": "batlit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13490257"}}]